Matcha is a variety of green tea, the only difference is that it is grown and processed differently than standard green tea. Matcha is rich in antioxidants, hence it is a very good detoxifier and may help protect your liver health. Ingredients Preparation Step 1 In a glass, mix Matcha powder and small amounts of water until all is dissolved. Step 2 Fill the glass with ice cubes Step 3 Top it with milk then add the sweetener (syrup). Step 4 Add in the Matcha mix and stir Enjoy with your favourite croissant! 